---------------------------------------
Set up steps for Angular Application
---------------------------------------

1. Create a folder in any location and name it as helloworld_angular_app
2. Download the QuickStart-Angular zip file as provided
3. Copy and paste it in the helloworld_angular_app folder, from the download location
4. Unzip the quick-start
5. Go inside the folder and select all files. 
6. Paste in helloworld_angular_app folder and delete the quickstart_angular zip and folder that was created during unzipping. 

-----------------------------------------------------
Now run below commands to clear all unwanted files. 
-----------------------------------------------------
1. open the command prompt and go inside the helloworld_angular_app folder
2. run below command one by one
for /f %i in (non-essential-files.txt) do del %i /F /S /Q
rd .git /s /q
rd e2e /s /q

-----------------------------------------------------------
Now run below command to run the application
-----------------------------------------------------------
1. open the command prompt and go inside the helloworld_angular_app folder
2. run below command one by one

npm install;
npm start;

your application will be launch on http://localhost:3000
